creator: Igor Luchkin
descriptionHtml:
SimpleWordConverter can convert Microsoft Word documents (DOC and DOCX files) to other formats: HTML, TXT, PDF.

Application Features:
- Does not require an internet connection.
- Easy to use.

How to use:
Open the MS Word document from the main application menu or from the file manager context menu.
The application window displays the result of the conversion.
Then print or save the result as an HTML archive or text file.
If you want to save the result as a PDF document, then:
1) click the Print button
2) in the preview window, select Save as PDF instead of printer
3) press the round button "PDF"
descriptionShort: Simple converter of MS Word documents in HTML, TXT and PDF. Works offline.
